name: A Rose is a Rose, still
description: Exported image of "drawing machine 001", a generative, interactive software art piece, originally created in 2004 to create design elements for a CD cover, updated in June 2021. This image is the result of an interactive collaboration between the artist and the code that she wrote. Artwork by LIA (www.liaworks.com), 2021. Still: 3840 x 2160 pixel. Edition of 1 + 1 AP  (not minted).
